outputPhase_MR/chr1.phase.o_freqs : haplotype frequency estimates
outputPhase_MR/chr1.phase.o_pairs : most likely haplotype pairs for each individual
outputPhase_MR/chr1.phase.o_recom : estimates of recombination parameters
outputPhase_MR/chr1.phase.o_monitor : file for monitoring convergence
END OUTFILE_LIST

